body.description: The boost your child will love. Loaded with comfort features for kids, the Graco® TurboBooster® 2.0 Highback Booster Seat helps protect your growing child, from 40-100 lb. This 2-in-1 booster seat converts from a highback to a backless booster as your big kid grows. Kids will love cool perks like the hide-away cup holders and comfort features, especially the height-adjustable head support and height-adjustable armrests. Parents will love that it helps protect their child by raising them up to the proper height for the seat belt. The open-loop belt guides help properly position the vehicle seat belt to allow for independent self-buckling. This seat is Graco® ProtectPlus Engineered™ to help protect your child in frontal, rear, & rollover crashes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The Graco TurboBooster Highback Booster Seat in Glacier is a stellar choice for parents seeking safety, comfort, and versatility in a car seat!The highback feature provides excellent head and neck support, offering a secure seating option for growing kids. The Glacier design is sleek and stylish, adding a touch of sophistication to the car interior.Installation is a breeze, and the adjustable headrest ensures a snug fit as my child grows. The seat is not only comfortable but also offers peace of mind with its safety features, making it a reliable choice for every journey.I appreciate the durability and easy-to-clean design, crucial factors for parents on the go. The cup holders are a thoughtful addition, making road trips a little more convenient.Overall, the Graco TurboBooster Highback Booster Seat has exceeded my expectations. It's a fantastic investment in my child's safety and comfort during car rides. Highly recommended for parents looking for a reliable and stylish booster seat option!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pros and Cons
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to purchase them a reliable booster seat for car rides that wouldn't break the bank, so I opted for the popular Graco TurboBooster. After using it extensively, here is my list of pros and cons.Pros:- Easy, secure installation: The straightforward installation provides peace of mind from the start. Securing the seat with the vehicle belt takes just minutes and gives a sturdy, shake-free fit.- Adjustable for growing kids: The high back adds protection in case of side impacts while the headrest and height adjustments grow with my kiddo.- Portable for transfers between vehicles: Literally just grab and go because its lightweight.- Budget-friendly cost: Compared to other brands, the price was economical and competitive.Cons:- Fabric stains over time- Less side cushioning than premium brands- Kids complain about comfort on very long drivesIf you're seeking reliable protection for your kids without overspending, the user-friendly Graco TurboBooster ticks all the boxes. Safety above all, but value matters too - this seat delivers both. Hope this review helped.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Safety and Comfort Combined - A Parent’s Best Friend
reviews.reviewText: The Graco TurboBooster Highback Booster Seat in Glacier has quickly become an essential part of our family’s daily life. As parents, safety and comfort for our children are paramount, and this booster seat delivers on both fronts seamlessly.What we love most about this booster seat is its simplicity. Installation is a breeze, and the highback design provides an extra layer of protection and comfort. The Glacier design is sleek and neutral, making it easy to fit into any car interior.As our child grows, the adjustable headrest and height positions ensure that they are always secure and comfortable during our journeys. It’s reassuring to know that our little one is safely strapped in while we focus on the road ahead.Furthermore, the TurboBooster’s portability is a game-changer. We can easily transfer it between vehicles without any hassle, making it incredibly convenient for busy families on the go.In summary, the Graco TurboBooster Highback Booster Seat in Glacier is a reliable, comfortable, and user-friendly addition to our family. It provides us with the peace of mind that our child is safe during car rides, and its convenience factor is a huge plus. We couldn’t be happier with this purchase.If you’re a parent looking for a top-notch booster seat, the Graco TurboBooster in Glacier is a fantastic choice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We purchased two of these in 2021, not for twins but to have one in each car for our son. Lately, a second one has come in handy for being able to get his friend to/from school sometimes. The removable back is perfect for those who are on the smaller side and will be using a booster for longer. The seatbelt holder is easy to use and makes it simple to go from one car to the other. The cup holders are easily accessible for the young ones to use on their own. For those who are about to make the switch from a car seat, this is a great booster to go with.
